ComicInfo.Summary:
Rogue: A dinosaur has killed two miners and Jack is hired to prevent the dinosaur from threatening the lives of other miners and from jeopardizing mining operations.
Mammoth Pitfall: While trying to trap a mammoth, Jack and Hannah are ambushed by Hammer Terhune.
The Rules of the Game: Jack and Hannah go for a joyride, but a storm arises. In an effort to outrun the storm, and the subsequent flooding, Jack crashes his vehicle. Seeking shelter from the storm, Jack and Hannah find refuge in the strangest of places.
